Name: Deltazone
About the game: Join our DISCORD Server for more updates. DELTAZONE drops players into an unprecedented global conflict that has been going on for a few years. Your mission is to wipe out the opposing team and take back the land that was once yours. Your fate depends on your skill Base game includes: - DeathMatch - Team DeathMatch - Domination - Bomb More GameModes will be added Either as DLC or base content. This will be decided in a later date. You will be able to join players that host DLC Maps/GameModes, You just cant host matches with those specific Maps/GameModes.
